{"tid":589722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（估國家）攞正牌放假！政府頒令周日不可以做生意，屢犯者監都有得坐","createTime":"2018-03-12T05:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T12:23:00.000Z","uid":22675,"like":95,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"13b48b20f7904c96df6d34cdea0f5851fed04615","tid":589722,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:02:39.000Z","msg":"攞正牌放假！波蘭頒令周日不可以做生意<br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/130211_dc2b8ab8a6ae5032351eda525a18ae00.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F130211_dc2b8ab8a6ae5032351eda525a18ae00.png&h=59a64471&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外媒報道，波蘭周日生意禁令生效，大部分商店不得於周日營業，除了加油站，咖啡店，雪糕店，藥店和某些其他企業例外，另機場和火車站的商店也被允許開放。 <br />\n<br />\n為使社會慢慢適應，法例將分階段實施，於2018年每月的其中2個周日實施，2019年則於每月其中3個周日，直至2020年全面實行。任何違反新規則的人都可能面臨高達10萬茲羅提(約23萬港元)的罰款，而屢犯者可能面臨監禁。 <br />\n─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─"},{"pid":"563ea3743910e680ec8927578460da91f7e75e9a","tid":589722,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:04:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7efa231b29b4b773108e36dd1884bbc4aa30cfb","tid":589722,"uid":35430,"like":78,"dislike":3,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:05:14.000Z","msg":"港柒：冇競爭力，垃圾，懶鬼，國家窮，福利主義整死經濟，佔中問題"},{"pid":"a91bd65dde5c45577b6d8f70afcb31d17aa4903b","tid":589722,"uid":35430,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:06:56.000Z","msg":"股市急挫樓價下跌，破產，周身債，廢柴國家，唔挨得，想當年我游水，歐豬"},{"pid":"0f093557d6088fe5c4833e4a9374a28d952d9eb3","tid":589722,"uid":35430,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:09:24.000Z","msg":"我地好顧家，為公司，拼搏，同甘，共渡，工賊會"},{"pid":"6c463761a0c833c5082de715e7fb2eedc7e7166a","tid":589722,"uid":35430,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:09:44.000Z","msg":"等滅國啦波蘭"},{"pid":"2390025c6504b82bfff599220d2eaebba905a693","tid":589722,"uid"